<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: blind fog -->
  <BlindFog.label>迷雾</BlindFog.label>
  <!-- EN: A heavy fog that reduces the accuracy of ranged weapons, as well as their maximum range. -->
  <BlindFog.description>浓雾会降低远程武器的精度和射程。</BlindFog.description>
  <!-- EN: Blind fog -->
  <BlindFog.letterLabel>迷雾</BlindFog.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A thick fog is setting in, dramatically reducing vision. Ranged weapons will be less accurate and their maximum range will be reduced. -->
  <BlindFog.letterText>浓雾开始笼罩，大幅降低了能见度。远程武器的精度和射程都将降低。</BlindFog.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: blizzard -->
  <Blizzard.label>暴雪</Blizzard.label>
  <!-- EN: Snow reduces the accuracy of ranged weapons, extinguishes fire, and slows people down. -->
  <Blizzard.description>暴雪会降低远程武器的命中率，扑灭火焰，同时还会降低移动速度。</Blizzard.description>
  
  <!-- EN: orbit -->
  <Orbit.label>轨道</Orbit.label>
  <!-- EN: There is no weather in orbit. -->
  <Orbit.description>轨道上没有天气。</Orbit.description>
  
  <!-- EN: overcast -->
  <Overcast.label>阴天</Overcast.label>
  <!-- EN: Thick clouds obscure the sky, reducing light levels. -->
  <Overcast.description>浓云遮蔽天空，降低了光照强度。</Overcast.description>
  
  <!-- EN: sandstorm -->
  <Sandstorm.label>沙暴</Sandstorm.label>
  <!-- EN: Sandstorms reduce the accuracy of ranged weapons, slow people down, and get sand everywhere. -->
  <Sandstorm.description>沙暴会降低远程武器的精度、减缓人员移动速度，还会让沙子无处不在。</Sandstorm.description>
  
  <!-- EN: torrential rain -->
  <TorrentialRain.label>暴雨</TorrentialRain.label>
  <!-- EN: Torrential rain causes flooding. It also reduces the accuracy of ranged weapons, extinguishes fire, and slows people down. -->
  <TorrentialRain.description>暴雨会导致洪水，还会降低远程武器的命中率，扑灭火焰，同时还会降低移动速度。</TorrentialRain.description>
  <!-- EN: Torrential rain -->
  <TorrentialRain.letterLabel>暴雨</TorrentialRain.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: Heavy rain is beginning to pour from the sky. It will cause temporary flooding around bodies of water. Build barriers to prevent floodwater from spreading. -->
  <TorrentialRain.letterText>暴雨从天空中倾泻而下。水域周围会出现短时洪涝。请建造障碍物以防止洪水蔓延。</TorrentialRain.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: tox rain -->
  <ToxRain.label>毒雨</ToxRain.label>
  <!-- EN: Tox rain makes creatures sick with toxic buildup. It also reduces the accuracy of ranged weapons, extinguishes fire, and slows people down. -->
  <ToxRain.description>毒雨会使生物中毒，还会降低远程武器的命中率，扑灭火焰，同时还会降低移动速度。</ToxRain.description>
  <!-- EN: Tox rain -->
  <ToxRain.letterLabel>毒雨</ToxRain.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: Toxic rain has begun to fall from the sky. It will slowly sicken anyone it touches. Keep your colonists under a roof. -->
  <ToxRain.letterText>有毒的雨水从天而降，暴露于其中会逐渐中毒。让你的殖民者待在屋檐下。</ToxRain.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: windy -->
  <Windy.label>强风</Windy.label>
  <!-- EN: Strong winds reduce movement speed. -->
  <Windy.description>强风会降低移动速度。</Windy.description>
  
</LanguageData>